Package: DoseOptDesign
Title: Utility Score Framework for Dose Optimization Studies
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xuemin", "Gu", 
           email = "xuemin.gu@bicycletx.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Cong", "Xu", role = "aut"),
    person("Lei", "Xu", role = "aut"),
    person("Ying", "Yuan", role = "aut")
)
Description: Implements a utility score framework for dose optimization studies 
    with binary efficacy-safety endpoints. Provides sample size determination 
    using normal approximation and exact multinomial calculations, characterizes 
    selection-induced bias in two-stage designs, and quantifies Type I error 
    inflation in confirmatory analyses. Methods are described in Gu et al. (2025) 
    <arXiv:2603.15884>.
